E.  Required Outputs and Reports 

13.  The consultant will complete the following: 

(i)  inception report 1 month after commencement of consulting services; 
(ii)  macroeconomic and sector study 3 months after commencement of consulting 
services; 
(iii)  poverty reduction and social strategy and summary of poverty reduction and 
social strategy 3 months after commencement of consulting services; 
(iv)  report on assessment of Lae port 3 months after commencement of consulting 
services; 
(v)  technical site investigations, technical feasibility study, and preliminary design 
including contract packages, procurement plan, and implementation schedule 3 
months after commencement of consulting services;  
(vi)  financial assessment, cost estimates, and project financial analysis 3 months 
after commencement of consulting services; 
(vii)  socioeconomic  analysis  and  project  economic  analysis  3  months  after 
commencement of consulting services;  
(viii)  environmental  impact  assessment  and  summary  environmental  impact 
assessment 3 months after commencement of consulting services; 
(ix)  a resettlement plan 3 months after commencement of consulting services; 
(x)  project  design  and  monitoring  framework  and  baseline  data  3  months  after 
commencement of consulting services; 
(xi)  a report on public consultation and a table of external assistance to the port 
sector in PNG 3 months after commencement of consulting services; 
(xii)  interim report 4 months after commencement of consulting services; 
(xiii)  detailed  engineering  design  and  bidding  documents  5  months  after 
commencement of consulting services; and 
(xiv)  draft final report 5 months after commencement of consulting services, and final 
report 11 months after commencement of consulting services.
